xxl.core.indexStructures

Class MVBTPlus.Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.indexStructures.Tree.Node
      • xxl.core.indexStructures.BPlusTree.Node
        • xxl.core.indexStructures.MVBTree.Node
          • xxl.core.indexStructures.MVBT.Node
            • xxl.core.indexStructures.MVBTPlus.Node
  • Enclosing class:
    MVBTPlus

    public class MVBTPlus.Node
extends MVBT.Node
    This is a MVBT node implementation. Note that MVBTPlus maps i node to a O(B) number of physical blocks. Maximal number of pages one index node can span is 6, if default settings used. Leaf nodes have one-to-one mapping to blocks.
